<P>VER. 1. <HI>Oh Happine&s;s!</HI> &amp;c.] in the MS. thus,</P>
<LG>
<L>Oh Happine&s;s! to which we all a&s;pire,</L>
<L>Wing'd with &s;trong hope, and borne by full de&s;ire;</L>
<L>That ea&s;e, for which in want, in wealth we &s;igh;</L>
<L>That ea&s;e, for which we labour and we die.</L>
