<LG>
<L>Say not, "Heav'n's here profu&s;e, there poorly &s;aves,</L>
<L>"And for one Monarch makes a thou&s;and &s;laves."</L>
<L>You'll find, when Cau&s;es and their Ends are known,</L>
<L>'Twas for the thou&s;and Heav'n has made that one.</L>
