</LG>
<LG>
<L>Riches, like in&s;ects, when conceal'd they lie,</L>
<L N="170">Wait but for wings, and in their &s;ea&s;on fly.</L>
<L>Who &s;ees pale Mammon pine amid&s;t his &s;tore,</L>
<L>Sees but a backward &s;teward for the Poor;</L>
<L>This year a Re&s;ervoir, to keep and &s;pare;</L>
